result.name: phase-2a-west-midlands-to-crewe
result.notes:
Phase 2a West Midlands to Crewe GIS data

The data provided here relates to information and/or engineering design described within the High Speed Rail (West Midlands to Crewe) Environmental Statement deposited in Parliament as part of the hybrid Bill deposit in July 2017, Supplementary Environmental Statements & Additional Provisions. Accessing the data in these formats may require specialised equipment, programmes or products. The data does not form part of the ES. It is not necessary to be able to access or view the information in these formats in order to participate in the ES consultation.

organization.name: high-speed-2
organization.title: High Speed 2 Limited
organization.description:
High Speed Two Limited (HS2 Ltd) is responsible for developing proposals for a new national high speed rail network. It is a company limited by guarantee and wholly funded by grant-in-aid from the government.

HS2 is an executive non-departmental public body of the Department for Transport

http://www.hs2.org.uk/
